                    <li><b>Everlasting Memories –</b> The memories you make together as a family on a trip are evergreen. These memories help shape good thoughts and outlook on life overall.</li>
                    <li><b>More the merrier –</b> The more people you are travelling with the more exciting and unique your trip is going to be. Together embarking on new adventures is something that is much more thrilling than solo adventures.</li>
                </ol>
